wukong!’s commands¶

admin¶

command

description

usage

aliases

lang

changes the server language

w!lang <language code>

setlang

prefix

change the server prefix

w!prefix <new prefix>

setprefix

developer¶

command

description

usage

aliases

eval

evaluates js

w!eval <javascript code>

none

msgchannel

sends message to a channel

w!msgchannel <channel id> <message>

none

msgdm

sends message to an id’s dm

w!msgdm <user id> <message>

none

togglepremium

toggle premium for a server

w!togglepremium <server id>

none

userblacklist

toggle blacklist for user id

w!userblacklist <user id>

blacklistuser

editbalance

edit someone’s balance

w!editbalance <user id> <amount>

addbal

fun¶

command

description

usage

aliases

emojify

turns text into copypasta

w!emojify <text>

emojipasta

enchantify

turns text into enchantment table

w!enchantify <text>

enchant

randomcase

randomcases text

w!randomcase <text>>

rc

reverse

reverses text

w!reverse <text>

none

general¶

command

description

usage

aliases

avatar

get someone’s avatar

w!avatar <mention>

pfp, picture, icon

calc

calculates math expression

w!calc <math expression>

math

help

get information about command

w!help <command>

commands, usage

info

bot statistics

w!info

botstats, botinfo

invite

wukong!’s invite url

w!invite

none

premium

check server premium status

w!premium

vip

roles

list of all roles in the server

w!roles

none

server

support server invite

w!server

support

servericon

get the server icon

w!servericon

serverpfp

serverinfo

get information about the server

w!serverinfo

none

profile

see someone’s profile

w!profile <mention>

userprofile, pr

balance

check your balance

w!balance

bank, atm, money
